<section class="hero"> 
<div class="container">
  <div class="car1">
    <picture>
      <source media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="/src/assets/img/bg-intro-desktop.svg"  />
      <img src="/src/assets/img/bg-intro-mobile.svg" alt="Background" class="fondo">
    </picture>
      <img src="/src/assets/img/image-mockups.png" alt="celulares" class="encim">
  </div>


<div class="car3 encima">
  <h1>Next generation digital banking</h1>
  <p>Take your financial life online. Your Easybank account will be a one-stop-shop for spending, saving, budgeting, investing, and much more.</p>
  <button class="btn">Request Invite</button> 
</div>

</div>



<div class="car2">
  <h1>Why choose Easybank?</h1>
  <p>We leverage Open Banking to turn your bank account into your financial hub. Control your finances like never before.</p>
</div>

<div class="lin">
<div class="car3">
  <figure>
    <img src="/src/assets/img/icon-online.svg" alt="icon online" class="icono">
  </figure>
  <h1>Online Banking</h1>
  <p>Our modern web and mobile applications allow you to keep track of your finances wherever you are in the world.</p>
</div>

<div class="car3">
  <figure>
    <img src="/src/assets/img/icon-budgeting.svg" alt="icon budgeting" class="icono">
  </figure>
  <h1>Simple Budgeting</h1>
  <p>See exactly where your money goes each month. Receive notifications when you’re close to hitting your limits.</p>
  
</div>

<div class="car3">
  <figure>
    <img src="/src/assets/img/icon-onboarding.svg" alt="icon onboarding" class="icono">
  </figure>
  <h1>Fast Onboarding</h1>
  <p>We don’t do branches. Open your account in minutes online and start taking control of your finances right away.</p>
 
</div>

<div class="car3">
   <figure>
    <img src="/src/assets/img/icon-api.svg" alt="icon api" class="icono">
  </figure>
  <h1>Open API</h1>
  <p>Manage your savings, investments, pension, and much more from one account. Tracking your money has never been easier.</p>
</div>

</div>


</section>

<style>


.car1{
  position: relative;
  height: 330px; /* controla el recorte */
  overflow: hidden;
}


.car2{
   display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 3rem 2rem 0rem 2rem;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
.car2 h1{
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  padding: 0 1.4rem;
}
.car2 p{
  color: hsl(233, 8%, 62%);
  font-size: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}


.fondo{
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;

  
  
}
.encim{
  position: absolute;
  top: 28%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 93%;
  height: auto;
}

.car3{
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 1rem 2rem;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
.car3 h1{
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  padding: 0 1.4rem;
}
.car3 p{
  color: hsl(233, 8%, 62%);
  font-size: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.btn{
  background-color: hsl(136, 64%, 51%);
  color: white;
  border: none;
  padding: 0.6rem 2.5rem;
  border-radius: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.icono{
  width: 60px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  justify-content: center;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {


.car1{
  position: relative;
  height: 400px; /* controla el recorte */
  overflow: hidden; 
}
.fondo{
height: auto;
transform: scale(2.2) translate(22%, 3%); 
}



.encim{
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  resize: 10%;
 
  transform: scale(1.1) translate(-35%, -52%); 
  width: 110%;
  height: auto;

}
.container{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  direction: rtl;


}

.lin{
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;

}
  
}
.car3, p, h1{
  display: flex;
  text-align: left;
  align-items: flex-start;
  justify-content: left;

}
.car3{
  padding:0;
}
.encima{
  display: flex;
  text-align: center;
  align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 0px 15%;
}


.encima h1{
  padding:0;
}


</style>